s that make your WooCommerce site function properly. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The wishlist feature of WooCommerce allows your customers to choose products from your website and add them to a list to purchase them later. It also allows the customers to share the products with their friends through the social media platform. Hence, the wishlist has become an important part of any eCommerce website in the present context. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>WooCommerce Wishlist Plugins</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Given below is the list of popular WooCommerce wishlist plugins that you allow the users that visit your page to add items to a wishlist to save it for later purchase or share with their close friends or family. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>YITH WooCommerce Wishlist </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"828\" height=\"274\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Wishlist-2.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Wishlist \" class=\"wp-image-9131\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Wishlist-2.png 828w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Wishlist-2-300x99.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/YITH-WooCommerce-Wishlist-2-768x254.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 828px) 100vw, 828px\" title=\"10+ Best Free WooCommerce Wishlist Plugins 28\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Wishlist is the best free WooCommerce wishlist plugin that you can choose for your online store. This plugin allows the customers to save their favorite products and lets them find them quickly and easily at the time of buying. With more than 70K+ active installing, it is the most popular wishlist plugin that you can choose for your online store. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can purchase the premium version of the plugin in £90 for a single site. For six sites, the plugin costs £199.99, and for 30 sites, the plugin costs £199.99. However, you can download the free version of the plugin as well. The features offered by the free version of the plugin are awesome too.  </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Select a page for wishlist </li><li>Select where to add the shortcode &#8216;Add to Wishlist&#8217;</li><li>Customize columns to be displayed to wishlist table</li><li>Product variation support </li><li>View the wishlists creates by logged-in customers</li><li>Enable/disable the wishlist features for unlogged users</li><li>Allows users to manage, rename, add and remove wishlist </li><li>Allows users to manage the item quantity in the wishlist </li><li>Shows product price variations</li><li>Allow users to move an element from one wishlist to another</li><li>Choose modern &amp; beautiful layouts</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2>TI WooCommerce Wishlist </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large image-shadow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"841\" height=\"275\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TM-WooCommerce-Wishlist-1.png\" alt=\"TM WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin ss\" class=\"wp-image-9133\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TM-WooCommerce-Wishlist-1.png 841w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TM-WooCommerce-Wishlist-1-300x98.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/TM-WooCommerce-Wishlist-1-768x251.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 841px) 100vw, 841px\" title=\"10+ Best Free WooCommerce Wishlist Plugins 29\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ti WooCommerce Wishlist allows your customers to create wishlists and add products to them as per the demand of the users. This plu