u can choose the package of £149 and £249 respecitively. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>WPML Compatible </li><li>Product SKY in the compare table</li><li>Product image in compare widget </li><li>Social Media Integration </li><li>Easily customizable product comparison table</li><li>Shows related products on the product comparison page</li><li>Allows to compare products based on categories</li><li>Limits the number of products on the comparison table </li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2>WooCommerce Products Compare</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized image-shadow\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/WooCommerce-Products-Compare.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Products Compare Plugin ss\" class=\"wp-image-9083\" width=\"983\" height=\"748\" title=\"10+ Best Free WooCommerce Products Compare Plugins 56\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>WooCommerce Products Compare is a plugin by WooCommerce that allows the customers visiting an online store to compare prices as well as other features of the products on the store and choose among the best. With this plugin, you can compare products directly from the category pages. Also, this plugin helps to display a detailed comparison table. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Select products to compare</li><li>Comparison widget </li><li>Compare products directly on category pages</li><li>Show detailed comparison tables</li><li>Add comparison option anywhere on the store</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://wor